%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESarah%20Friar%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20it's%20hard%20to%20describe%20what%20it%20feels%20like%20to%20use%20the%20company's%20closely-guarded%20AI%20hardware%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20very%20natural%2C%20but%20it%20feels%20very%20lovable%2C%26quot%3B%20Friar%20said%20during%20a%20live%20interview%20at%20the%20%26quot%3BAll-In%20Podcast%26quot%3B%20team's%20Liquity%20Summit%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20co-hosts%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BAll-In%26quot%3B%20podcast%20pressed%20her%20on%20whether%20Jony%20Ive-led%20device%20is%20an%20earpiece%2C%20she%20joked%20about%20the%20legendary%20iPhone%20designer's%20potential%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20tell%20you%20it's%20an%20earpiece%2C%20Jony%20will%20come%20and%20steal%20my%20teenage%20son%2C%26quot%3B%20Friar%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20might%20give%20him%20to%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FTjrShuj_Zsg%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22OpenAI%20CFO%20Sarah%20Friar%20on%20IPO%2C%20AI%20Rivalries%2C%20New%20Device%2C%20and%20Spending%20%24100B%2B%20on%20Compute%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EFriar%20described%20a%20visceral%20reaction%20to%20using%20the%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Johnny%20and%20team%20are%20really%20good%20at%20is%20bringing%20humanity%20to%20devices%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20really%20know%20how%20to%20explain%20that%20well%2C%20but%20when%20you%20see%20it%2C%20you%20feel%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20has%20remained%20largely%20mum%20about%20what%20the%20device%20will%20be%2C%20leading%20to%20rampant%20speculation%20online.%20In%20February%2C%20OpenAI%20quickly%20denounced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-fake-super-bowl-ad-alexander-skarsgard-dime-device-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epurportedly%20leaked%20ad%20featuring%20actor%20Alexander%20Skarsg%C3%A5rd%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20showed%20an%20orb-shaped%20device%20and%20earbuds%20as%20%26quot%3Btotally%20fake.%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20said%20the%20device%20is%20not%20a%20phone%2C%20ending%20one%20line%20of%20speculation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20more%20certain%20is%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-timeline-hardware-ai-device-launch-jony-ive-iyo-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20the%20timeline%20for%20OpenAI's%20launch%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20its%20first%20hardware%20device.%20Friar%20said%20that%20she%20has%20already%20tried%20out%20the%20device.%20She%20said%20that%20by%20%26quot%3Bthe%20end%20of%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20will%20unveil%20the%20device.%20Previously%2C%20OpenAI%20said%20in%20a%20legal%20filing%20that%20it%20did%20not%20expect%20to%20ship%20the%20device%20until%20February%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202025%2C%20OpenAI%20announced%20it%20was%20buying%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findustries-openai-is-disrupting-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EIve's%20AI%20hardware%20startup%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20IO%2C%20for%20roughly%20%246.5%20billion.%20Altman%20and%20Ive%20also%20said%20they%20were%20working%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bfamily%20of%20AI%20products.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFriar%20said%20great%20design%20can%20make%20technology%20feel%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnology%20can%20be%20very%20mechanistic%2C%20but%20we%20all%20know%20great%20design%20just%20makes%20everything%20fade%20away%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3Bthe%20simple%20is%20hard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20and%20Ive%20previously%20said%20they%20want%20consumers%20to%20find%20the%20device%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-jony-ive-lick-test-openai-device-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eso%20irresistible%20that%20they%20want%20to%20eat%20it.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20he%20said%20once%20early%20on%2C%20we'll%20know%20we%20have%20the%20design%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said%20in%20November%20during%20an%20onstage%20event%20with%20Ive.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20remember%20whether%20he%20said%2C%20when%20you%20want%20to%20lick%20it%20or%20take%20a%20bite%20out%20of%20it%2C%20or%20something%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-cfo-ai-device-jony-ive-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780510102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a205cc9b4fb977f35983cd1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-cfo-ai-device-jony-ive-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20CFO%20Sarah%20Friar%20said%20she%20can't%20say%20if%20the%20Jony%20Ive-led%20device%20is%20an%20earpiece.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Firhad%20Hakim%2C%20Close%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20Aide%20Who%20Quit%20As%20Kolkata%20Mayor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Firhad%20Hakim%2C%20who%20also%20represents%20the%20Kolkata%20Port%20constituency%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20was%20a%20loyalist%20of%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20in%20politics.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780510057000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2