quot%3B%20by%20a%20lawmaker's%20call%20to%20shrink%20its%20proposed%20AI%20campus%20by%2075%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKevin%20O'Leary%20has%20defended%20the%20project%20as%20a%20job%20creator%20and%20a%20major%20piece%20of%20AI%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20proposal%20has%20drawn%20backlash%20over%20its%20scale%2C%20water%20use%2C%20and%20energy%20demands.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-oleary-ai-data-center-backlash-ben-thompson-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKevin%20O'Leary's%3C%2Fa%3E%20company%20says%20it%20was%20caught%20off%20guard%20by%20a%20Utah%20lawmaker's%20demand%20to%20dramatically%20shrink%20its%20proposed%20AI%20data%20center%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Utah%20Senate%20President%20J.%20Stuart%20Adams%20said%20he%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20celebrity%20investor%20calling%20for%20a%2075%25%20reduction%20in%20the%20proposed%20data%20center%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdams%20%E2%80%94%20who%20also%20chairs%20the%20Military%20Installation%20Development%20Authority%2C%20which%20gave%20the%20project%20an%20initial%20approval%20in%20April%20%E2%80%94%20wrote%20that%20he%20wants%20the%20Box%20Elder%20County%20data%20center%20to%20be%20reduced%20from%2040%2C000%20acres%20to%20about%2010%2C000%20acres.%20He%20also%20said%20he%20wanted%20stronger%20commitments%20on%20water%2C%20conservation%2C%20environmental%20review%2C%20heat%20reduction%2C%20and%20public%20transparency%20before%20the%20project%20moves%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20engaged%20any%20Utah%20legislators%20on%20this.%20The%20letter%20caught%20us%20off%20guard%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20O'Leary%20Digital%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20is%20that%20we%20are%20analyzing%20the%20letter%20carefully%20with%20our%20team%2C%20and%20Kevin%20intends%20to%20respond%20to%20President%20Adams%20personally%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Stratos%20Project%20is%20a%20proposed%20AI%20and%20defense%20data%20center%20campus%20in%20Box%20Elder%20County%2C%20Utah's%20extreme%20northwestern%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EState%20documents%20describe%20it%20as%20a%20large-scale%20data%20and%20energy%20campus%20meant%20to%20support%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20cloud%20computing%2C%20and%20defense%20operations.%20If%20built%20at%20its%20current%20proposed%20scale%2C%20the%20campus%20would%20require%207.5%20to%209%20gigawatts%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20data%20center%20projects%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Leary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sltrib.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2F2026%2F06%2F01%2Fkevin-oleary-says-hes-not-walking%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20Salt%20Lake%20Tribune%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20walking%20away%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20project%20and%20called%20the%20proposed%20reduction%20%26quot%3Boutrageous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20the%20deal%20I%20had%20with%20Adams.%20That's%20not%20what%20we%20agreed%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BCutting%20back%20the%20deal%2075%25%20is%20like%20me%20selling%20you%20a%20house%2C%20and%20you%20get%20to%20live%20in%20the%20upstairs%20toilet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FUK_2A_RHGfc%3Fsi%3DDCD3OudQbqrXozaV%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20Stratos%20Project%20has%20become%20a%20flash%20point%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-oleary-accused-data-center-critics-chinese-agent-utah-