3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20notched%20a%20strong%20of%20record%20highs%20and%20has%20gained%20double%20digits%20since%20the%20start%20of%202026%2C%20despite%20headwinds%20like%20the%20Iran%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FrkI1e%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20on%20Wall%20Street%20have%20drawn%20comparisons%20between%20today's%20market%20and%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%2C%20where%20an%20unsustainable%20rise%20in%20stock%20prices%20outpaced%20earnings%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20dot-com%20era%2C%20BCA%20said%20today's%20AI%20bubble%20is%20driven%20by%20unsustainable%20earnings%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22988a93a5-3529-47af-8cd5-6daa834494ee%5C%22%3EEarnings%20bubbles%20through%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20old%20adage%20goes%2C%20history%20often%20rhymes%2C%20and%20BCA%20called%20out%20some%20historic%20parallels%20to%20today's%20market%20landscape.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerezin%20flagged%20the%20stock%20moves%20in%20the%20lead%20up%20to%20the%20Great%20Financial%20Crisis%20as%20an%20example%20of%20an%20earnings-driven%20bubble.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20P%2FE%20ratios%20remained%20low%2C%20disguised%20by%20an%20unsustainable%20increase%20in%20profits%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20more%20recent%20instance%20of%20an%20earnings%20bubble%20burst%20was%20the%20work-from-home%20beneficiaries%20in%202020%20and%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarnings%20bubble%20are%20more%20common%20in%20industries%20that%20see%20boom%20and%20bust%20cycles.%20%26quot%3BThese%20industries%20include%20natural%20resources%2C%20airlines%2C%20shippers%2C%20and%20importantly%20for%20today's%20environment%2C%20semiconductors%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20strategist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bd1025b3-a073-4158-83af-5dcb23547f07%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20today's%20AI%20bubble%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFirst-quarter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-record-high-rally-investing-strategy-wall-street-stocks-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eearnings%20results%20astounded%20Wall%20Street%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20AI%20trade%20revived%20by%20a%20string%20of%20stellar%20results.%20BCA%20noted%20that%20supply-demand%20imbalances%20are%20among%20the%20main%20factors%20propping%20up%20earnings.%20A%20major%20example%20has%20been%20in%20t%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmemory-stocks-rally-chips-tech-stock-market-investing-sndk-mu-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20memory-stock%20trade%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20exploded%20this%20year%20as%20AI%20drives%20up%20demand%20for%20memory%20storage%20in%20the%20latest%20phase%20of%20AI%20development.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShortages%20lead%20to%20higher%20prices%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20lead%20to%20fatter%20profit%20margins.%20Higher%20profits%20incentivize%20investment%20in%20new%20capacity.%20Supply%20eventually%20catches%20up%20to%20demand%2C%20causing%20prices%20and%20profits%20to%20plunge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fai-capex-boom-meta-microsoft-amazon-alphabet-goldman-sachs-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espending%20billions%20on%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20infrastructure%20buildout%20is%20driving%20huge%20demand%20for%20hardware.%20Shortage-driven%20profits%20are%20ultimately%20driving%20stocks%20to%20new%20all-time%20highs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20paradoxical%20situation%3A%20Aggregate%20free%20cash%20flow%20among%20the%20hyperscalers%20is%20crashing%20and%20could%20turn%20negative%20in%202027.%20Yet%2C%20reported%20profits%20are%20going%20through%20the%20roof.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBCA%20warned%20that%20another%20factor%20for%20investors%20to%20consider%20the%20expected%20depreciation%20in%20value%20of%20what%20Big%20Tech%20is%20currently%20pouring%20money%20into.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed56e426-ea89-45fb-8ca5-320aeefdf536%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20AI%20bubble%20will%20burst%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strategist%20sounded%20the%20alarm%20that%20Wall%20Street%20is%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20an%20AI%20bubble%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20it's%20about%20to%20pop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20all%20bubbles%2C%20the%20AI%20bubble%20will%20burst.%20For%20now%2C%20however%2C%20our%20AI%20demand%20indicators%20do%20not%20suggest%20that%20this%20is%20imminent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20note%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20BCA%20still%20sounded%20a%20warning%20for%20the%20market.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarnings%20bubbles%20can%20be%20more%20toxic%20for%20the%20economy%20than%20valuation%20bubbles%20if%20they%20leave%20an%20overhang%20of%20excess%20capacity%20in%20their%20wake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%20AI%20trade%2C%20that%20means%20that%20if%20the%20tech%20isn't%20as%20widely%20adopted%20as%20expected%2C%20massive%20AI%20spending%20will%20have%20a%20negative%20ripple%20effect%20on%20the%20broader%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20of%20an%20earnings%20bubble%20compared%20to%20a%20typical%20valuation%20bubble%2C%20is%20that%20analysts%20don't%20start%20cutting%20profit%20estimates%20until%20after%20stocks%20decline%2C%20BCA%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-bubble-ai-record-highs-earnings-ai-investing-stocks-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780506244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a204550b4fb977f35983ba7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-bubble-ai-record-highs-earnings-ai-investing-stocks-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20stock%20market%20has%20rallied%20to%20record%20highs%20on%20stronger-than-expected%20Q1%20results%2C%20but%20Wall%20Street%20might%20be%20overlooking%20a%20growing%20earnings%20bubble.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nbuchanan%40insider.com%20(Naomi%20Buchanan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A95%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kick%20streamer%20Clavicular%20chased%20a%20new%20look%20through%20live%20rhinoplasty%20and%20left%20viewers%20speechless%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780506165000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131488663%2Cimgsize-1959246.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fkick-streamer-clavicular-chased-a-new-look-through-live-rhinoplasty-and-left-viewers-speechless%2Farticleshow%2F131488685.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131488685.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ELooksmaxxing%20streamer%20Braden%20Peters%2C%20known%20as%20Clavicular%2C%20livestreamed%20his%20rhinoplasty%20on%20Kick%20on%20June%203%20with%20celebrity%20plastic%20surgeon%20Dr.%20Michael%20Salzhauer%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Dr.%20Miami.%20The%20surgery%20lasted%20about%20two%20hours%20and%20drew%20nearly%206%2C000%20average%20viewers.%20The%20broadcast%20quickly%20went%20viral%2C%20with%20some%20viewers%20intrigued%20and%20others%20uncomfortable%20watching%20cosmetic%20surgery%20live.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sehjal%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fkick-streamer-clavicular-chased-a-new-look-through-live-rhinoplasty-and-left-viewers-speechless%2Farticleshow%2F131488685.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fkick-streamer-clavicular-chased-a-new-look-through-live-rhinoplasty-and-left-viewers-speechless%2Famp_articleshow%2F131488685.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fkick-streamer-clavicular-chased-a-new-look-through-live-rhinoplasty-and-left-viewers-speechless%2Famp_articleshow%2F131488685.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Western%20air%20forces%20have%20used%20centralized%20headquarters%20for%20decades.%20A%20top%20NATO%20commander%20said%20this%20easy%20era%20is%20over.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NATO%20allies%20have%20centralized%20their%20operations%20at%20large%20airfields%20like%20RAF%20Lakenheath%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20where%20these%20F-35%20Lightning%20II%20fighters%20are%20based.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1ee8b1b4fb977f3598345c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225461%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENATO%20allies%20have%20centralized%20their%20air%20operations%20into%20a%20small%20number%20of%20combined%20air%20operations%20centers%2C%20and%20that%20needs%20to%20change%2C%20a%20top%20official%20said.%3Cp%3EStaff%20Sgt.%20Elizabeth%20Davis%2FUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20growing%20number%20of%20air%20threats%20means%20the%20West%20shouldn't%20rely%20on%20a%20few%20major%20headquarters.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20large%20command%20post%20is%20a%20target%20%E2%80%94%20just%20as%20are%20aircraft%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20runways.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20top%20NATO%20commander%20said%20that%20these%20command%20centers%20must%20be%20broken%20up%20and%20become%20mobile.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20West's%20long-enjoyed%20luxury%20of%20having%20large%20command%20centers%20can't%20continue%2C%20even%20though%20it%20will%20make%20work%20more%20difficult%2C%20a%20top%20NATO%20commander%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20has%2C%20for%20decades%2C%20operated%20out%20of%20large%20air%20operations%20centers%2C%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESir%20John%20Stringer%2C%20NATO's%20Deputy%20Supreme%20Allied%20Commander%20Europe%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20honest%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20still%20looks%20like%20it%20did%20towards%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20two%20decades%20even%20with%20the%20Cold%20War.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20can't%20continue%20as%20the%20number%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fera-west-guaranteed-control-skies-over-uk-air-official-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethreats%20in%20the%20air%20grows%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said.%26quot%3BThe%20sense%20of%20the%20big%20single%20air%20operation%20center%2C%20which%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20grown%20up%20with%20over%20the%20last%20sort%20of%2035%20years%20%E2%80%94%20probably%20first%20seen%20at%20scale%20in%20the%20Gulf%20War%20in%201991%20%E2%80%94%20through%20to%20the%20fixed%20command%20and%20reporting%20centers%2C%20that's%20going%20to%20have%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Stringer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20needs%20to%20be%20mobility%20in%20command%20instead%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20mobility%2C%20redundancy%2C%20and%20survivability%20in%20command%20and%20control%20are%20essential.%20Those%20are%20not%20going%20to%20%3Cem%3Ebecome%3C%2Fem%3E%20essential.%20They're%20essential%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20it%20as%20an%20area%20where%20NATO%20needs%20to%20%26quot%3Bplay%20catch-up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENATO's%20current%20large%20air%20operation%20centers%20include%20the%20Combined%20Air%20Operations%20Center%20at%20Uedem%2C%20Germany%2C%20which%20directs%20and%20monitors%20NATO%20missions%20with%20aircraft%20like%20Dassault%20Rafales%20and%20F-16%20fighter%20jets%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20is%20responsible%20for%20all%20of%20the%20alliance's%20air%20policing%20in%20northern%20Europe%2C%20including%20in%20the%20Baltic%20region%2C%20where%20the%20threat%20from%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-nato-air-policing-mission-fighter-pilots-minutes-scramble-jets-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussia%20is%20the%20strongest%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Another%20center%2C%20in%20northern%20Norway%2C%20oversees%20missions%20across%20the%20Baltic%20Sea%20and%20the%20Nordic%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20decades%2C%20the%20Western%20way%20of%20running%20air%20wars%20has%20focused%20on%20a%20small%20number%20of%20large%20command-and-control%20organizations%20like%20these%20that%20coordinate%20aircraft%20sorties%2C%20missile%20strikes%2C%20surveillance%2C%20air%20defense%20operations%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20works%20extremely%20well%20when%20an%20adversary%20doesn't%20have%20the%20range%20to%20target%20them%2C%20but%20that's%20likely%20not%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-air-force-now-more-dangerous-nato-learned-ukraine-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efuture%20wars%20will%20look%20like%3C%2Fa%3E.%20China%20and%20Russia%2C%20for%20example%2C%20have%20built%20huge%20missile%20arsenals%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-using-new-jet-powered-drone-response-interceptors-ukraine-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eare%20leading%20producers%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20attack%20drones%2C%20as%20well%20as%20less%20advanced%20adversaries%20like%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20will%20make%20NATO's%20work%20harder%2C%20Stringer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGetting%20everybody%20in%20one%20place%20is%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20distributed%20it%20becomes%2C%20the%20more%20difficult%20and%20challenging%20it%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20means%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bessential%26quot%3B%20investment%20in%20modern%20communication%20and%20information%20systems%20to%20coordinate%20that%20work%2C%20Stringer%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20necessity%20to%20disperse%20command%20cells%20echoes%20a%20wider%20strategic%20shift.%20Large%20air%20bases%20like%20RAF%20Lakenheath%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20Ramstein%20in%20Germany%20could%20become%20targets%20for%20missile%20and%20drone%20barrages%2C%20where%20runway%20damage%20could%20prevent%20aircraft%20from%20taking%20off%20and%20become%20sitting%20ducks%20on%20the%20tarmac.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224091%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20member%20of%20the%20Combined%20Air%20Operations%20Centre%20Uedem%20wears%20a%20patch%20inside%20a%20P-8A%20Poseidon%20maritime%20patrol%20aircraft.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f2519b4fb977f359836db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222727%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20member%20of%20the%20Combined%20Air%20Operations%20Centre%20Uedem%20wears%20a%20patch%20inside%20a%20P-8A%20Poseidon%20maritime%20patrol%20aircraft.%3Cp%3ELt.%20Sara%20Wedemeyer%2FUS%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20drawbacks%2C%20communication%20will%20need%20to%20work%20in%20a%20more%20networked%20way%2C%20he%20said%2C%20with%20command-and-control%20functions%20spread%20across%20multiple%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20future%20mission%20set%2C%20for%20example%2C%20may%20spread%20headquarters%20tasks%20from%20mission%20planning%20to%20tactical%20control%20across%20widely%20separated%20bases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20look%20like%20different%20headquarters%20and%20ships%2C%20and%20aircraft%2C%20rather%20than%20concentrated%20in%20a%20single%20headquarters%20or%20operations%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20something%20NATO%20has%20been%20testing.%20When%20Stringer%20served%20as%20deputy%20commander%20of%20NATO's%20Allied%20Air%20Command%2C%20it%20started%20practicing%20how%20to%20distribute%20its%20command%20functions%20to%20get%20%26quot%3Baway%20from%20one%20single%20center%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EStringer%20is%20also%20a%20former%20senior%20officer%20in%20the%20UK's%20Royal%20Air%20Force%2C%20where%20he%20flew%20aircraft%20including%20the%20SEPECAT%20Jaguar%20and%20the%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20something%20NATO%20tests%20in%20big%20exercises%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat's%20very%20much%20a%20focus%26quot%3B%20for%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20alliance's%20command%2C%20Stringer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nature%20of%20Ukraine's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-did-russia-invade-ukraine-putin-politics-motive-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efight%20against%20Russia's%20invasion%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20sparked%20a%20flurry%20of%20warnings%20across%20the%20alliance%20that%20militaries%20also%20need%20to%20start%20dispersing%20in%20other%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDispersal%20and%20mobility%20have%20been%20key%20to%20Ukraine's%20survival%2C%20from%20the%20very%20start%20of%20Russia's%20full-scale%20invasion%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20kept%20Ukraine's%20far%20smaller%20air%20force%20from%20being%20wiped%20out.%20A%20US%20general%20said%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-targeting-cant-catch-ukraine-air-force-top-us-general-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUkraine%20lost%20relatively%20few%3C%2Fu%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20its%20aircraft%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20the%20first%2018%20months%20because%20%26quot%3Bthey%20very%20seldom%20will%20take%20off%20and%20land%20at%20the%20same%20airfield.%26quot%3B%20Russia%20took%20longer%20to%20disperse%20aircraft%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-attacked-russian-jets-at-base-fighter-bombers-disperse-to-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUkraine%20was%20able%20to%20destroy%3C%2Fa%3E%20many%20of%20them%20clustered%20on%20airfields%20and%20at%20air%20bases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20even%20finding%20ways%20to%20keep%20its%20US-made%20F-16s%20on%20the%20move%2C%20so%20they%20don't%20need%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-new-way-keep-f-16s-moving-strategy-west-looking-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erely%20on%20the%20advanced%20airfields%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20among%20Russia's%20priority%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20lesson%20many%20Western%20officials%20and%20analysts%20say%20the%20West%20needs%20to%20adopt%20%E2%80%94%20and%20quickly.%20Gen.%20Kevin%20Schneider%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20US%20Pacific%20Air%20Forces%2C%20said%20last%20year%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20days%20of%20operating%20from%20secure%2C%20fixed%20bases%20are%20over.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20threats%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20required%20%26quot%3Ba%20flexible%2C%20resilient%20force%20that%20can%20operate%20from%20multiple%2C%20dispersed%20locations%20under%20contested%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoing%20that%20makes%20the%20job%20harder%3A%20A%20large%20air%20base%20has%20fuel%2C%20maintenance%2C%20and%20control%20facilities%2C%20and%20dispersing%20makes%20every%20step%20more%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20also%20keeps%20air%20defense%20assets%2C%20command%20centers%2C%20and%20key%20units%20on%20the%20move%20and%20concealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20war%2C%20especially%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20drone%20war%2C%20is%20like%20a%20cat-and-mouse%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Taras%20Berezovets%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20military%20cooperation%20department%20of%20Ukraine's%20Territorial%20Defense%20Forces%2C%20said%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Ukrainian%20defense%20manufacturers%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-starting-produce-nato-state-away-from-russia-attacks-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espread%20their%20production%20%3C%2Fa%3Eacros