ding%20their%20children%20to%20school%20instead%20of%20making%20them%20work.%20Many%20of%20these%20children%20did%20odd%20jobs%20and%20spent%20their%20earnings%20on%20tobacco%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CConvincing%20parents%20and%20children%20was%20a%20battle.%20I%20begged%20at%20times%2C%20I%20reasoned%20at%20others%2C%20and%20I%20kept%20asking%20them%20to%20send%20their%20children%20to%20school%20at%20least%20one%20more%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlowly%2C%20her%20persistence%20paid%20off.%20Within%20a%20month%2C%20attendance%20rose%20to%20100%20students.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20an%20easy%20victory%3B%20it%20meant%20knocking%20on%20doors%20daily%2C%20challenging%20traditions%20of%20child%20labour%2C%20and%20winning%20the%20trust%20of%20parents%20who%20had%20never%20experienced%20the%20benefits%20of%20education%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETeaching%20beyond%20textbooks%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20children%20began%20attending%20regularly%2C%20a%20new%20challenge%20emerged%3A%20holding%20their%20attention.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sangeeta%20employs%20innovative%20teaching%20methods%2C%20such%20as%20incorporating%20songs%20and%20interactive%20activities%20to%20make%20learning%20enjoyable.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1